{"tid":2399952,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"女歌手爆被逼上酒店陪笑！險被經紀人性侵淚崩「想跳下樓」","createTime":"2021-02-08T13:54:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T15:10:07.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a489b8e4d21330e6d1ae7bd465555242120d5efa","tid":2399952,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T13:54:07.000Z","msg":"光鮮亮麗的南韓娛樂圈近年多次爆出暗黑潛規則的新聞，近日，23歲的偶像歌手姜勝妍（音譯，강승연）就在節目上坦言，過去有差點被經紀人性侵的經驗，讓她既崩潰又害怕，還一度想不開。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/02/08/3021224-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F02%2F08%2F3021224-PH.jpg&h=f9edb479&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲23歲的偶像歌手姜勝妍。（圖／翻攝自푸하하TV YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n姜勝妍外型甜美，在螢光幕上看來活潑開朗，但其實私下為了圓歌手夢遭遇不少心酸事，在5日的《深夜神堂》中，姜勝妍透露，為了實現夢想，曾四處去造訪大大小小的經紀公司，邊練習歌唱技巧邊等待出道機會，但有一次卻被公司的人帶到酒店參加飯局，讓她相當驚慌失措。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/02/08/3021223-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F02%2F08%2F3021223-PH.jpg&h=d0d6a1fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼姜勝妍為了夢想遭遇很多心酸事。（圖／翻攝自푸하하TV YouTube）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/02/08/3021226-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F02%2F08%2F3021226-PH.jpg&h=a1810db8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除此之外，姜勝妍21歲時曾經跟某位經紀人簽下1對1合約，當時去到很遠的外縣市跑場演出，當時投宿在汽車旅館，原本還想經費不足也沒辦法，只能將就下度過一晚。但經紀人卻對她動了邪念，差點被性侵的姜勝妍害怕不已，當下甚至還萌生了：「還是我乾脆從這裡跳下去？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/02/08/3021225-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F02%2F08%2F3021225-PH.jpg&h=38636bb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲姜勝妍的故事讓觀眾看得很心疼。（圖／翻攝自푸하하TV YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n姜勝妍坦言，從小就看著爸爸毆打媽媽的場景，所以很討厭回家，也深刻體認到只有自己可以守護自己，在幫媽媽報警後就決定搬出來獨自生活。「現在幾乎沒跟爸爸聯絡了，媽媽則是再婚遇到很好的人很幸福」，想到姜勝妍開朗笑容下的心酸往事，讓觀眾都直呼心疼。"},{"pid":"31f5215c817eee580b19ba7028599709c4569418","tid":2399952,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T13:55:02.000Z","msg":"最憎依啲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚賤 <br />\n要人賣肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f060226b8670243aedd9305343a9f0716267e959","tid":2399952,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T13:56:54.000Z","msg":"想保護佢地...打拾啲色狗..<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fe629e07b5ab4e6170a928aa83ddedcf685b8e4","tid":2399952,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T13:57:37.000Z","msg":"彩瑛？"},{"pid":"09bd4cdbbbb42cf24e9223a6385bd32e36db633c","tid":2399952,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f060226b8670243aedd9305343a9f0716267e959","tid":2399952,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T13:56:54.000Z","msg":"想保護佢地...打拾啲色狗..<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T13:57:41.000Z","msg":"我先夠打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e76d4e2e2fc90cd023a567234959a65cc0e66673","tid":2399952,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fe629e07b5ab4e6170a928aa83ddedcf685b8e4","tid":2399952,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T13:57:37.000Z","msg":"彩瑛？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T13:57:56.000Z","msg":"U<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a203b18511108e8709b8b57ba33bca7d5501b36d","tid":2399952,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,